<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>jiān dìng gēn cóng 迦南875</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhù fú xiōng dì jiān dìng gēn cóng, zhù fú jiě mèi yǒng bù huī xīn.
 tiān fù bì kàn gù, shèng líng bì zhǐ yǐn. yé sū shì wǒ men de hǎo mù rén.
 kào jìn zhǔ jìng wèi shén, bù yào pà tóu dǐng shàng yǒu wū yún.
 zhǐ guǎn kāi kǒu tiān tiān zàn měi shén. zhǔ bì gěi nǐ kāi chuán dào de mén.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>875</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>